race.comment: DARLING SECRET (10) followed an unplaced effort first-up two runs back with a second last start over 302m at this track after being in the firing line on the bend. Finds a suitable race and can go on to take this out. FIRE IN MY BLOOD (2) finished third at Sam Houston Park two runs back but was less effective last time over 320m at Gillespie County Fairground (Dirt), finishing 3.5 lengths back in eighth. Has started two times at this course and distance and is yet to miss the placings. Facing a tougher assignment but he is up to the task. ONE FINE WINE (3) disappointed last time when seventh over 402m at this track (Dirt) after a close second at Retama Park (Dirt) the run prior. Better suited at this shorter trip so he is one of the main contenders. MR CHILES (6) has not appeared since he finished third over 320m at Turf Paradise (Dirt) on February 25. Among the better hopes.
